  "title": "Release scripts should be runnable from develop",
  "body": "Right now when we release new versions in which we update the release scripts, we have to manually update the `master` branch and then launch the release scripts. This is because the `master` never has the latest build scripts, but this could be solved if we were running the scripts from the `develop` branch.",
